## 8. Risk Assessment

### What Can Break in Production

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Scenario |
|------|-----------|--------|----------|
| **Attendance data confusion (FN/AN)** | HIGH | HIGH | Admin marks via webpanel (always FN), teacher marks via mobile (AN) — two records per student per day confuses reports |
| **Dashboard timeout on large schools** | HIGH | MEDIUM | 7 parallel full-data fetches for weekly chart with 500+ students |
| **Teacher sees all classes** | HIGH | MEDIUM | `/auth/me` returns empty `assignedClasses` → teacher sees every class in the school |
| **Weak default passwords exposed** | MEDIUM | HIGH | `FirstName@123` pattern is guessable if `requirePasswordChange` isn't enforced on webpanel |
| **Accountant/Principal role lockout** | HIGH | HIGH | Users created with these roles cannot access any API endpoint |
| **Sequential attendance submission timeout** | MEDIUM | HIGH | Webpanel bulk attendance for 50+ students fires 50 sequential requests |

